task.summary:
Adding 'users' page. Each user is added by his email address and can receives an email with unique link to reset his password and gain access.
Limiting the adding/deleting of branches and users to 'admin'. Showing error messages on delete and add.
Fixing bugs in 'reset password email' procedure. Server is made more responsive and explanatory whern db error happens.
Employees record now have start and end of contract date, which enables users to apply non-destructive updates, particularly when the hourly rate is changed in a particular date
